methods.readAdoString:
Read a String from the supplied input using DataInput.readUTF(), converting result Strings that match a
 single null character ("\0") to null.

:param in: (java.io.ObjectInput) - The input
:return: (java.lang.String) The resulting String after null conversion
methods.writeAdoString:
Write a String to the supplied output using DataOutput.writeUTF(String), encoding null values as
 Strings of a single null character ("\0").

:param out: (java.io.ObjectOutput) - The output
:param value: (java.lang.String) - The value to write

text: Utilities for generated code and related classes.
